{"tid":1354632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請求中国快D制裁香港啦!","createTime":"2019-07-23T07:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T07:09:49.000Z","uid":198175,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4236df4c30234efc0d74b63926522d4e1c555901","tid":1354632,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:30:36.000Z","msg":"721班港獨竟然嚟中聯辦搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反中亂港! 大逆不道!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吃我的飯砸我的鍋!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請求中国政府快D制裁香港啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7個即時制裁令<br />\n即時停止再俾自由行同旅遊團去香港旅遊消費, 唔好俾錢香港人賺!<br />\n即時停止內地專材來香港, 淘空國內人材, 不要助長香港經濟發展!<br />\n即時停止每日150個單程証到港, 愛國就要留在中国建設祖國!<br />\n即時停止沪/深港通股票自由行, 救中国股市, 沽爆港股!<br />\n即時停止国企民企在香港上市, 回歸A股!<br />\n即時停止国企民企經由香港銀行融資, 不要讓香港銀行賺我們的錢!<br />\n即時停止投資香港房地產, 沽爆港樓, 等班香港人個個負資產!<br />\n<br />\n同意請廣傳, 好人一生平安!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a769fb408efa51ec30e480e99fdf1dbdf276ada0","tid":1354632,"uid":52928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T07:34:31.000Z","msg":"8964"},{"pid":"816f3fb3ef12620c4a3f1c608fbe2017770425ed","tid":1354632,"uid":198175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:06:42.000Z","msg":"帝吧的同志快进來!"},{"pid":"9f653800b9c3828e62c32f60316e6f3d14eeb631","tid":1354632,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:13:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3fcd8b44de2a67cc2df006afe6ead039993a8bb1","tid":1354632,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:27:29.000Z","msg":"中国快D懲罰香港啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417c0389b21f822ad2319ab67185